    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<div class=\"alert alert-warning\">\n  <strong>Note:</strong> please note that Liferay has renamed its Liferay Experience\n  Could offerings to <i><strong>Liferay SaaS</strong></i> (formerly LXC) and\n  <i><strong>Liferay PaaS</strong></i> (formerly LXC-SM).\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HBB3N3CZTRFQP88XJ9FHGPZ6\">Added</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>[SFS] Backups should not include adaptive media, thumbnails and previews</li>\n<li>[Backup] Release Adaptive Media filtering for Liferay SaaS only</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HBB3N3CZ0TNGG189VXCA9DS9\">Bug</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>VPN deletion is leaving vpn-1 pending removal</li>\n<li>The lcp scale command allows a user to scale above the plan’s allowed number of instances using the CLI</li>\n<li>Nodegit crashes when pushing back big error messages</li>\n<li>Add value field to scope Support readonly</li>\n</ul>"
      },
